{"tid":1633751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登大量分化撚出沒注意","createTime":"2019-10-07T05:05:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T05:27:10.000Z","uid":30246,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"07bf3dd649488d7b88a4b43da2e2ef38cf5592dc","tid":1633751,"uid":30246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:05:50.000Z","msg":"連登大量分化撚出沒<br />\n根本你做乜都屌<br />\n出又屌唔出又屌<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力<br />\n你認為邊種做法可以撼動中共政權就去做<br />\n唔需要分和理非同勇武<br />\n和勇目標係一致，只不過方法唔同<br />\n真正既同路人係唔會指責手足<br />\n即使唔同意手足做法<br />\n但我地一定會理解手足點解要咁做<br />\n<br />\n如果真係睇到啲post 覺得唔舒服<br />\n我建議你唔好上連登<br />\n上facebook twitter都好過上連登<br />\n<br />\n大家仲記唔記得運動初期既原則<br />\n不分化，不割蓆，不篤灰<br />\n團結先係我地贏既唯一出路"},{"pid":"62bec50dd49062b3144cc056cba3fa395cbaf6fc","tid":1633751,"uid":26827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:06:29.000Z","msg":"勇武和理一人讓一步 再次合一！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633482\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633482</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9bc2ec012442c546ed75109fd9292dc31a5b4c76","tid":1633751,"uid":167011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:07:07.000Z","msg":"罷工係對個政權最撚有衝擊既抗爭手法，但三罷做左咁撚多次，都係得8.5成功，因為計劃左好撚耐，對香港人黎講，個個都只想被罷工，到呢個地步，你仲想做休息撚，而唔乘勝追擊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勿拆黨鐵！！全民被罷工！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n三樣香港人應同樣憎恨既野：<br />\n政府、黑警、黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n呢三樣先係主線<br />\n你個啲乜鳩紅藍店，我理撚得你幾時搞？<br />\n個啲要休息，冇問題，但咁撚樣都唔食住上，令到全港自動罷工，咁我真係代表我全力支持既香港政府多謝你為香港既經濟服務<br />\n<br />\n唔撚係話和理非冇用，但勇和齊上齊落，兩邊一齊做唔撚得？"},{"pid":"5c3a1c35a10223ee990324f004c2fb02452c8216","tid":1633751,"uid":247940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:07:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b609e5a1c76bb489f6a9a43bfd5be2ea83d5d4ca","tid":1633751,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:07:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"82e62619f7bea1177565d8350a9e2452581c0331","tid":1633751,"uid":30246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:08:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"75ea2703e29ee4e70033266e0731b9e9672a0692","tid":1633751,"uid":30246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:10:22.000Z","msg":"不分化"},{"pid":"b3d7bc121f1d8c1a95f82e6d31b345f5730240bf","tid":1633751,"uid":30246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:10:33.000Z","msg":"不篤灰"},{"pid":"ab54aafe8c6f47c9256b1105d05c0715262fc417","tid":1633751,"uid":30246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:10:44.000Z","msg":"不割蓆"},{"pid":"1644141a0edb46545bbeed9e41252f833997fb71","tid":1633751,"uid":42549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:11:10.000Z","msg":"香港人一定要團結<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到底邊個最想以後取消百萬大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633735</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2eb16232e1a31c7bb23ed28356bbfa8497e89997","tid":1633751,"uid":159762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:13:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港警察濫權實錄資料庫</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftl.hkrev.info%2Fpolice-timeline&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4rc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=027e1c69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tl.hkrev.info/police-timeline</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">仲有英文同日文版 大家落力share俾更多外國人睇！！</span>"},{"pid":"9b9a9f5cac90fbee1f2e96aa3792f1928c31c842","tid":1633751,"uid":186851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:14:47.000Z","msg":"總之連登好多狗帶風向"},{"pid":"d8496c4d301d04ba5e74142270c269cce98c4236","tid":1633751,"uid":290878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":